"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Hate\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Truffle_Oil&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Truffle Oil is an option for the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Purple.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/24px-Bundle_Purple.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/36px-Bundle_Purple.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#Artisan_Bundle\" title=\"Bundles\">Artisan Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Bundles#Pantry\" title=\"Bundles\">Pantry</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crafting\">Crafting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Truffle_Oil&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Crafting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Truffle Oil is used to make the following items:\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Image\n</th>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n<th>Ingredients</th>\n<th>Recipe Source(s)</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Rain_Totem.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rain Totem.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Rain_Totem.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Rain_Totem\" title=\"Rain Totem\">Rain Totem</a>\n</td>\n<td>Activate to greatly increase the chance for rain tomorrow. Consumed on use.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Hardwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/24px-Hardwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/36px-Hardwood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Hardwood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Hardwood\" title=\"Hardwood\">Hardwood</a>&#160;(1)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Truffle Oil.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3d/Truffle_Oil.png/24px-Truffle_Oil.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3d/Truffle_Oil.png/36px-Truffle_Oil.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/3d/Truffle_Oil.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Truffle Oil</a>&#160;(1)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Pine Tar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ce/Pine_Tar.png/24px-Pine_Tar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ce/Pine_Tar.png/36px-Pine_Tar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ce/Pine_Tar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>&#160;(5)</span>\n</td>\n<td><div class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Foraging Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Foraging_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Foraging_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Foraging_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Foraging_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Foraging_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Foraging_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Foraging#Foraging_Skill\" title=\"Foraging\">Foraging</a> Level 9</div>\n</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0020\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"20\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />20g</span>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Truffle_Oil&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Without the <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Artisan Profession</a>, iridium quality <a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">truffles</a> are worth more to sell outright rather than turn into oil.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Truffle_Oil&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Truffle Oil can be used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the dyeable <a href=\"/File:Shirt262a.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt262a.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/85/Shirt262a.png/24px-Shirt262a.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/8/85/Shirt262a.png 1.5x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Dark Bandana Shirt</a>.  It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Truffle_Oil&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Mayor <a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a> requests Truffle Oil by mail on the 21st of <a href=\"/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a> (year 2) in the <a href=\"/Quests#Mayor.27s_Need\" title=\"Quests\">\"Mayor's Need\" Quest</a>.  The reward is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"750\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />750g</span> and 1 <a href=\"/Friendship\" title=\"Friendship\">Friendship</a> heart.<br />Note that Lewis will send the letter triggering the quest regardless of whether or not the player owns a <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">pig</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Truffle_Oil&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Now dropped by <a href=\"/Truffle_Crab\" title=\"Truffle Crab\">Truffle Crabs</a>. Now purchasable through <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a> • <a href=\"/Green_Tea\" title=\"Green Tea\">Green Tea</a> • <a href=\"/Juice\" title=\"Juice\">Juice</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil\" title=\"Oil\">Oil</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Truffle Oil</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Aged_Roe\" title=\"Aged Roe\">Aged Roe</a> • <a href=\"/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\">Caviar</a> • <a href=\"/Jellies_and_Pickles\" title=\"Jellies and Pickles\">Jellies and Pickles</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414153339\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.205 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.241 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3691/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 33666/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2983/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 16/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4160/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.008/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 744 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  129.330      1 -total\n 59.44%   76.878      1 Template:Infobox\n 20.93%   27.065      1 Template:EdibilityGrid\n 20.62%   26.663      2 Template:Description\n 16.74%   21.647      1 Rain_Totem\n 14.84%   19.194      1 Template:RecipeRow/NoBuffsHealthEnergy\n  9.90%   12.802      5 Template:Name\n  8.13%   10.518      4 Template:Overlayimg\n  7.05%    9.122      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  5.79%    7.489      2 Template:Qualityprice\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2099-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414153339 and revision id 181658\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng             = Truffle Oil\n|source          = [[Artisan Goods]] • [[Desert Festival]] • [[Truffle Crab]]s • [[Traveling Cart]]\n|ingredients     = {{name|Truffle|1}}\n|edibility       = 15\n|sellprice       = 1065\n|quality         = false\n|craftingstation = {{name|Oil Maker}}\n|crafttime       = 360m (6h)\n}}\n'''Truffle Oil''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made in the [[Oil Maker]] from a [[Truffle]], taking 6 hours to produce. It can also be dropped from [[Truffle Crab]]s. One may be purchased from [[Marnie]]'s [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|50|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s. Occasionally the [[Traveling Cart]] will offer it in her rotating stock.\n\nDespite being listed as \"A gourmet cooking ingredient\" there are no cooking recipes that use it, but it is used to make the [[Rain Totem]].\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n|hate=Sebastian,Jas,Vincent\n|love=Harvey\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nTruffle Oil is an option for the {{Bundle|Artisan||y}}.\n\n==Crafting==\nTruffle Oil is used to make the following items:\n{{Recipes|header|hide=restores,buff,duration}}\n{{:Rain Totem|RecipeRow/NoBuffsHealthEnergy}}\n{{Recipes|footer}}\n\n==Notes==\nWithout the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Artisan Profession]], iridium quality [[Truffle|truffles]] are worth more to sell outright rather than turn into oil.\n\n==Tailoring==\nTruffle Oil can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[File:Shirt262a.png|24px]] [[Tailoring|Dark Bandana Shirt]].  It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\n*Mayor [[Lewis]] requests Truffle Oil by mail on the 21st of [[Summer]] (year 2) in the [[Quests#Mayor's Need|\"Mayor's Need\" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|750}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.<br />Note that Lewis will send the letter triggering the quest regardless of whether or not the player owns a [[pig]].\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.6|Now dropped by [[Truffle Crab]]s. Now purchasable through [[Desert Festival]].}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Trüffelöl]]\n[[es:Aceite de trufa]]\n[[fr:Huile de truffe]]\n[[it:Olio di tartufo]]\n[[ja:トリュフオイル]]\n[[ko:송로버섯 오일]]\n[[hu:Szarvasgomba olaj]]\n[[pt:Óleo de trufas]]\n[[ru:Трюфельное масло]]\n[[tr:Yermantarı Yağı]]\n[[zh:松露油]]"
